---
/**
 * @file SilenceMoment.astro
 * @description One enforced beat of stillness between Vox memoriae (II) and the catalog of
 *  past concerts. When the sentinel reaches viewport center, Lenis stops, wheel + touchmove
 *  + scroll-keys are intercepted, the score marking "tacet." fades in, dwells for ~2.8s, then
 *  scroll resumes — once per browser session. The word is the moment: in a part-book, tacet
 *  instructs the voice to stay silent — here the page itself rests before the voice enters
 *  (VoxMoment follows). No attribution, no aphorism. Reduced-motion + no-JS visitors see the
 *  line statically (gated by html.voct-motion in landing.css).
 * @architecture Astro islands 2026
 * @module components/landing/SilenceMoment
 */
---

<section class="silence-moment" data-silence aria-label="Chwila ciszy">
  <div class="silence-sentinel" data-silence-sentinel aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="silence-inner">
    <svg
      class="silence-ornament"
      viewBox="0 0 120 12"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-linecap="round"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <line x1="0" y1="6" x2="50" y2="6" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-opacity="0.45" />
      <circle cx="60" cy="6" r="1.6" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
      <line x1="70" y1="6" x2="120" y2="6" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-opacity="0.45" />
    </svg>

    <p class="silence-line">
      <em>tacet.</em>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
